name: Gul Fiza
shortDescription: A collection inspired by geometric prints and patterns replicated to create a mesh effect.
longDescription: Inspired by geometric prints, Gulfiza motifs are a replication of patterns from everyday objects like baskets and mats, woven in grass and natural fibres  that lend the print a ‘Jaal’ (mesh) effect.  This range is available in rich jewel tones of pomegranate, aqua and jade.
